data.description: This well-built Lifestyle home in Highland Ranch is the 1696 Plan on a quiet cul-de-sack w more than a quarter-acre lot. It's close to shopping at the Spanish Springs Galleria. Step into the backyard and enjoy views of Peavine, Mt.Rose and Red Mountains. Mature trees on all sides provide wind breaks and summer shade while you enjoy the gazebo. Garden area with raised planter and NV Native flowers. Dog run and shed. RV gate/yard. Newer furnace w Honeywell air clean. No rear neighbors! Large concrete patio Home is 1696 sq ft, 3 bedroom 2 bath and is great for entertaining with a large living room, kitchen with lots of storage and dining room with vaulted ceilings. Primary bedroom is large and its bathroom offers dual sinks, separate water closet and shower/soaking tub combo with blue-tooth speaker to play your favorite songs while you relax. Garage features mounted cabinetry and workbench with pegboard, light fixtures and many outlets. Some cabinets in garage stay , one bench work area stays. Zoned for the new Hug High School!
